Maintained,by,BitPay,Bitcore,is,an,open,source,Node,js,library,for,creating,cross,platform,Bitcoin,enabled,applications,with,a,secure,payment,protocol,and,private,key,management,The,Bitcore,API,allows,a,method,of,Bitcoin,integration,using,JavaScript,The,API,specifically,enables,an,app,to,access,private,or,public,keys,perform,peer,to,peer,cryptocurrency,transactions,manage,networks,handle,and,convert,Bitcoin,and,more